data.text:
Philip Mulhall, 55, of Hope Mills, died Monday, April 16, 2018.

Born in Cumberland County, Philip was the son of the late James and Ilse Kahnert Mulhall.

Along with his parents, he was preceded in death by his sister, Ingrid Truman; brothers, James and John Mulhall; and stepson, James Tony Ross.

Philip is survived by his wife, Linda Mulhall; stepson, Brian Ross and wife Kristin of Fayetteville; granddaughter, Zoey Ross; and sister, Ilse Spaulding and husband Dan of Lillington.

In lieu of flowers the family suggest memorials be made to the American Heart Association/American Stroke Association, Memorial and Tribute Processing Center, 4217 Park Place Court, Gwen Allen, VA 23060.

Philip will be missed by all who knew and loved him.
